  "original_title": "\u0d9c\u0ddd\u0da8\u0dcf-\u0dbb\u0db1\u0dd2\u0dbd\u0dca \u0dba\u0db1 \u0dad\u0dd4\u0dbb\u0dd4 \u0dbb\u0da7 \u0db4\u0dd4\u0dbb\u0dcf \u0dc0\u0dd0\u0da9\u0dc0\u0dbb\u0dca\u0da2\u0db1, \u0dc4\u0dbb\u0dca\u0dad\u0dcf\u0dbd\u0dca",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "Nationwide strike, hartal till Gota-Ranil",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "Unions and mass organizations have said that they will initiate continuous strikes and hartals until the resignation of President Gotabhaya Rajapaksa and Prime Minister Ranil Wickremesinghe.",
        "Mr. Anupa Nandula, Senior Vice President of the Bank of Ceylon Employees Union, said that these professional measures are expected to be launched in the public and private sector workplaces across the country in the next few days.",
        "He also mentioned that professional action will have to be taken if they are not ready to accept the people's continuous demand that Mr. Gotabhaya Rajapaksa and Prime Minister Ranil Wickremesinghe should resign.",
        "Mr. Nandula also said that he would request them not to let it drag on until the trade union action, as they are still deeply disliked by the public.",
        "He said this while addressing a press conference held in Colombo by the Union of Trade Unions and Mass Organizations.",
        "He also mentioned that this time, professional measures will be taken which are more advanced than hartals, strikes and agitations which were implemented on April 28 and May 6."
      ],
